channel.itunes:summary: Girls Like Me - 10 comedy sketches by Morgan Brayton live from the Wise Hall. Combining storytelling and sketch comedy, Morgan introduces the audience to the world of women who live inside her head but frequently escape to make people laugh.
channel.description: Girls Like Me - 10 comedy sketches by Morgan Brayton live from the Wise Hall. Combining storytelling and sketch comedy, Morgan introduces the audience to the world of women who live inside her head but frequently escape to make people laugh. Meet middle-aged ! mom Button Bradley on the occasion of her first Women's Studies class. Root for nervous neophyte exotic dancer Cherry Lipsmacker as she takes to the stage for the first time. Have your license and registration ready because when Sgt. Tibble pulls you over, you will know you have been pulled over. And get a lesson in becoming a woman from Lizzie who learned about her fallopian tubes today at school.Find out what makes Morgan write haiku. Yes. There will be haiku.
